	dprr:hasNoteText "Q(uaestor?). In MRR 2.436, and Index, 548, refer also to Crawford, RRC 1.331, no. 332, 98 B.C. Both Crawford and Wiseman distinguish between two Cloelii, the second one probably being the Marian legatus of 83, and quaestor ca. 95 (Wiseman, CR 17, 1967, 263-264).\n" .
